A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 40-6-163 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to duty
2 of driver of vehicle meeting or overtaking school bus, reporting of violations, and civil
3 monetary penalty for violations captured by school bus camera, so as to revise the penalty
4 amount for violations captured by recorded images; to provide for related matters; to repeal
5 conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Code Section 40-6-163 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to duty of driver
9 of vehicle meeting or overtaking school bus, reporting of violations, and civil monetary
10 penalty for violations captured by school bus camera, is amended by revising subparagraph
11 (d)(3)(A) as follows:
12 "(A) The owner of a motor vehicle shall be liable for a civil monetary penalty to the
13 governing body of the law enforcement agency provided for in subparagraph (B) of this
14 paragraph if such vehicle is found, as evidenced by recorded images, to have been
15 operated in disregard or disobedience of subsection (a) of this Code section and such
